<i>noun</i>: 후덕 [후ː덕], 큰맘 [큰맘], 인자 [인자], 아량 [아ː량], 선심 [선ː심], 무욕 [무욕], 도량 [도ː량], 관용 [과뇽] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>후덕 [후ː덕]</dt><br>
<dd>virtue; generosity; benevolence</dd><br>
<dd>말과 행동, 성품 등이 어질고 덕이 후함.</dd><br>
<dd>One's words, action, and personality being virtuous and generous.</dd><br>
<dt>큰맘 [큰맘]</dt><br>
<dd>generosity; big heart</dd><br>
<dd>크고 넓게 생각하는 마음씨.</dd><br>
<dd>An attitude of thinking generously and open-heartedly.</dd><br>
<dt>인자 [인자]</dt><br>
<dd>benevolence; generosity; kindness</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 너그럽고 따뜻함. 또는 그 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being broad-minded and warm-hearted, or such an attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>아량 [아ː량]</dt><br>
<dd>tolerance; generosity</dd><br>
<dd>너그러운 마음씨.</dd><br>
<dd>A generous heart.</dd><br>
<dt>선심 [선ː심]</dt><br>
<dd>1. kind heart; virtuous attitude</dd><br>
<dd>착한 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>Kind heart.</dd><br>
<dd>2. mercy; generosity</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람을 돕거나 너그럽게 베푸는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>An inclination to help or provide favors to others.</dd><br>
<dt>무욕 [무욕]</dt><br>
<dd>generosity; unselfishness</dd><br>
<dd>욕심이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of having no greed.</dd><br>
<dt>도량 [도ː량]</dt><br>
<dd>1. generosity; broad-mindedness</dd><br>
<dd>너그럽게 받아들이고 깊게 이해할 수 있는 마음과 생각.</dd><br>
<dd>State of mind or thinking that can readily accept and deeply understand others.</dd><br>
<dd>2. calculation; measurement</dd><br>
<dd>길이, 부피, 무게 등을 재서 사물의 양을 헤아림.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of calculating the amount of something by measuring its length, volume, weight, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>관용 [과뇽]</dt><br>
<dd>tolerance; generosity</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 잘못을 너그러이 받아들이거나 용서함. 또는 그런 용서.</dd><br>
<dd>The capacity for generously forgiving or accepting another's mistakes, or a similar act of mercy.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>